  "description": "A nighttime view of a tiered fountain illuminated with purple and orange lights. The fountain is centrally located in a paved plaza, bordered by a low wall and greenery. In the background, a hillside rises, dotted with trees and a few buildings. The fountain\u2019s water jets create a dramatic, illuminated display. The plaza appears to be empty except for a faint figure next to the fountain. The overall scene is calm and visually striking, creating a pleasant, almost magical atmosphere.",
